	<style type="text/css">
		h1{font-size: 22px;}
		strong{color: red}
	</style>
	<script type="text/javascript">
		window.onload = function(){
			
			var searchString = "Now is the time and this is the time and that is the time";
			var re = /t\w{2}e/g;
			var repalcement = searchString.replace(re,"place");
			 
			document.getElementById("result").innerHTML = repalcement;

		}
	</script>
</head>
<body>
	<h1>패턴을 새로운 문자열로 치환하기</h1>
	<p>String 객체의 replace 메서드를 정규표현식과 함께 사용하면 됩니다.</p>
	<P>Now is the time and this is the time and that is the time</P>
	<div id="result"></div>
